            <title>[SOLR-1547] TemplateTransformer should copy array/list more intelligently</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1547</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;if a field is copied TemplateTransformer does a toString() &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;e.g&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;field column=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;id&quot;&lt;/span&gt;           template=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${slashdot.link}&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if slashdot.link is a List with a value &lt;a href=&quot;http://somelink/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://somelink/&lt;/a&gt; it would get copied as [ &lt;a href=&quot;http://somelink/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://somelink/&lt;/a&gt; ] &lt;/p&gt;</description>
